{"id": 8068, "source": "pestle", "subject": "chemistry", "course": null, "level": "HL", "paper": "1", "year": "2020", "session": "20N", "subtopic": "8-5-acid-deposition", "title": "20N.1.HL.TZ0.24", "topic_id": "8", "source_url": "https://pestle.pages.dev/app/", "question_html": "<div class=\"question\">\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Which of these oxides contribute to acid deposition?</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left:30px;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">I.  </span><math class=\"wrs_chemistry\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>SO</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><br/></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">II.  </span><math class=\"wrs_chemistry\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>NO</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><br/></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">III.  </span><math class=\"wrs_chemistry\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>CO</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">A.  I and II only<br/></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">B.  I and III only<br/></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">C.  II and III only<br/></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">D.  I, II and III</span></p>\n</div>", "solution_html": "<div class=\"question\">\n<p>A</p>\n</div>", "examiners_html": "<div class=\"question\">\n<p>Not well answered. Less than half knew which oxides contribute to acid deposition, with the majority including CO<sub>2</sub> in the list. This misconception was held by higher and lower scoring candidates equally.</p>\n</div>"}